description:
January 14, 2018 / Half a year after Bernard Howard was murdered, the police finally identified Terrance Lewis as a suspect after receiving a tip from a previously undisclosed source. At trial, though, the only evidence the prosecution used to make the case against Terrance and his co-defendants came from Star, the victim's girlfriend the first witness they spoke to.&#13;
&#13;
Episode scoring music by Animal Weapon, Blue Dot Sessions.&#13;
